    title: 'Third-Party Services & Links',
    paragraphs: [
      'The Website may include links to or integrations with third-party services (for example, scheduling, payment, or analytics providers). We are not responsible for the content, policies, or practices of those third parties. Your use of those services is subject to their own terms.',
